      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just not just \"emotions\" though. it's like... there's no light at the end of this. people say \"it gets better\" or \"stay strong\" but they don't get it. they don't understand that constant agony makes you feel like you're just waiting for permission to leave. sometimes it feels like the most merciful thing in the world would be to just not exist anymore. like, why is it considered wrong to want peace?",
